name: 罗万·朗格沃斯
name_full: 罗万·朗格沃斯 Rowan Longworth
introduction: Rowan Longworth resides in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada and attends public school. He has a younger brother Aiden Longworth and a younger sister Hannah Longworth. Rowan loves sports and plays soccer and hockey. His favourite video game is Minecraft. He likes photography and has been creating his own videos. He also likes spending time with his family and playing with his YorkiePom Yoshi. His favourite food is macaroni and cheese.
